    "Our search extended beyond academic publications to incorporate industry perspectives.",
    "Four relevant blogs were identified, which led to the exploration of 52 company websites.",
    "Additionally, reference lists of included studies yielded 15 further potential sources.",
    "From these 71 additional sources, 16 were inaccessible.",
    "After a detailed review of the remaining 55 sources, exclusions were made based on the criteria mentioned in Table 8."
